</colgroup>
<thead>
<tr>
<th class="tableblock halign-left valign-top">Setting</th>
<th class="tableblock halign-left valign-top">Explanation</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Language</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Select the language under <strong>Open language</strong> to enter the item texts in the selected language. The same language is automatically selected under <strong>Save language</strong>. In order to use the texts of one language in another language, select a different language under <strong>Save language</strong>.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Delete language texts</strong></p></td>
