<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Language selection</p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Select a language to enter a translation for the value. You can only enter details for characteristics of the type <strong>Text</strong>. The default language is displayed for editing by default.</p></td>
</tr>
