</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Back end icon</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">The default availability icons of the system are displayed here. These icons are set by default and can be replaced with individual icons.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Name</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Enter a name or description for the delivery period.</p></td>
</tr>
