<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Language</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Select the language from the drop-down list. The system language that was set when the system was first created is selected by default.</p></td>
