<li>
<p>Open the <strong>Default</strong> item.<br>
→ The <strong>Settings</strong> tab of the main variation opens.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Open the <strong>Properties</strong> tab.<br>
→ Any variation properties already linked to the variation are shown.</p>
